{"tid":868542,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"劈價實錄︰將軍澳富寧花園累減130萬沽 比同類單位低12.4%","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T05:17:53.000Z","uid":28245,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"01e087eeafaea7dd26070ecfb8541ed04d42c6d1","tid":868542,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"美聯林志堅表示，將軍澳富寧花園4座高層C室，實用面積592方呎，於今年8月首次於已補價自由市場，以710萬元放賣，放盤以來吸引不少買家睇樓，但超高叫價令準買家卻步，之後業主為求出貨，已不斷降價。 <br />\n<br />\n至本月中，業主將底價降至650萬元，但買家期望有較大減幅方會夠膽入市，基於外圍因素普遍不利樓價，業主最後決定減至580萬元賣出，呎價約9,797元。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，同面積5座低層K室，8月時成交價約662萬元，約兩個月內平82萬元，跌幅約12.4%。"},{"pid":"8c37e301f1f9d6d7469d2ff6685c20cd662d3842","tid":868542,"uid":28245,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"同樣價錢 今日將軍澳<br />\n明日啟德"},{"pid":"20da657526ab15baddab21f6b7e92faed8f350fa","tid":868542,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"將軍澳係新界, 唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0022b691b29ce48b29e649593b254ce5d74c4d8","tid":868542,"uid":37599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩個月高層平低層80幾萬<br />\n<br />\n不過新界居屋&hellip;"},{"pid":"f445e9c21a0e44aef1831890d809f6e69c66ecdb","tid":868542,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0022b691b29ce48b29e649593b254ce5d74c4d8","tid":868542,"uid":37599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩個月高層平低層80幾萬<br />\n<br />\n不過新界居屋&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10